    {
      "id": "node-1774880170104",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# How CUSUM is applied\r\n\r\nPipeline order (from source): \r\nsignals → BasicProcessor → trades → minimal_return filter → CUSUM filter → weights → label\r\n\r\n## CUSUM mechanics:                                                                                                         \r\nthreshold(t) = vol(t) × cusum_threshold × close(t)    [in price/dollar units]\r\naccumulate D[close] until sum > threshold → fire event, reset \r\n→ trade only survives if its entry_time hits a CUSUM event ",
      "x": -560,
      "y": -3515,
      "width": 1109,
      "height": 149,
      "nodeLabel": "N4"
    },
    {
