    {
      "id": "ai-1775056080671-780de0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1428,
      "y": -3043,
      "width": 473,
      "height": 436,
      "createdBy": "ai",
      "color": "5",
      "tags": [
        "skena",
        "project-log",
        "phase1"
      ],
      "text": "## 📋 Skena Project Log\n\n### Architecture Decisions\n- `vault://` URI scheme adopted — multi-vault support (`vault://v1/doc1.md`)\n- **Edge → frontmatter sync** dropped (canvas-only edges, no `.md` writes)\n- **Plotly outputs** — base64 image only for now; JSON rendering deferred\n- Cell nodes store content inline in `.canvas` JSON (no sidecar files)\n- Portal nodes: selected nodes MOVED to new `.canvas`, parent gets portal placeholder\n\n### Dev Environment\n- Remote: quant0 — Node.js v22.21.1, npm 10.9.4\n- VS Code Remote SSH; `extensionKind: [\"workspace\"]`\n- Webview URIs via `panel.webview.asWebviewUri()` — raw `file://` blocked\n\n### Phase 1 — Complete ✅\n- Canvas rendering: file, text, group, link, cell, chat, portal node types\n- LOD zoom levels (minimal → title only, detail → full content)\n- Drag/resize → debounced auto-save (500ms)\n- Cmd+click → opens file beside canvas\n- File drop from Explorer → new file node\n- Live file updates via `onDidSaveTextDocument`\n\n### Backlog / Good-to-have\n- `vault://notion/<page-id>` — Notion MCP integration (read-only)\n- AI chat nodes — Claude backend, pluggable (`claude | ollama | openai`)\n- Shiki bundle size: switch to `shiki/core` with explicit grammar imports\n\n### Phase 2 Next Steps\n- Cmd+Shift+A → fuzzy vault search QuickPick → add node\n- Configure `skena.vaults` in settings\n- `notion-client.ts` for Notion MCP URIs\n- Strip debug `console.log` statements",
      "nodeLabel": "N8"
    },
